{"version":1,"entries":{"person_115301_translations":{"at":1773369218341,"data":{"id":115301,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"福岛润 出生于日本爱媛县，日本男性配音员。隶属ARTSVISION，血型为O型。于日本播音演技研究所毕业，爱媛县出身。代表作有《琴浦小姐》真锅义久、《飙速宅男》鸣子章吉、《为美好的世界献上祝福！》佐藤和真。","name":"福岛润","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jun Fukushima is a Japanese voice actor and narrator who is affiliated with Arts Vision. He's been acting since the 1990s. He is sometimes confused with fellow Japanese voice actor Jun Fukuyama, as their name spellings are only different by one Kanji.","name":"Jun Fukushima","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"후쿠시마 준","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"福島潤","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"福島潤是日本的男性聲優。出身於愛媛縣，畢業於日本播音演技研究所，所屬公司為 ARTSVISION。","name":"福島潤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jun Fukushima","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Jun Fukushima es un actor de doblaje (seiyuu) y narrador japonés afiliado a Arts Vision. Ha estado actuando desde la década de 1990.\n\nA veces se le confunde con el también actor de doblaje japonés Jun Fukuyama, ya que la ortografía de sus nombres solo se diferencia en un kanji.","name":"Jun Fukushima","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дзюн Фукусима","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"จุน ฟุคุชิมะ","